						<summary>

						<p>Slab (second) of the ceiling in the Śiva temple.</p>						

						<p>This undated epigraph may be assigned to the 9th century, on the basis of palaeography and internal evidence of the record.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of one <hi rend="italic">maṟutu</hi> of land at Maḻavuru by Perbāṇadhirāju. The donees name is not mentioned.</p>						

						</summary>
